 итоговых строк?\"]}"},"done":true,"done_reason":"stop","total_duration":9229843400,"load_duration":120166300,"prompt_eval_count":295,"prompt_eval_duration":2147395000,"eval_count":110,"eval_duration":6667181000},7:headers;127:51:12:Content-Type,31:application/json; charset=utf-8,]40:4:Date,29:Sun, 19 Jul 2026 10:16:49 GMT,]24:14:Content-Length,3:988,]]12:http_version;8:HTTP/1.1,}7:request;2504:4:path;9:/api/chat,9:authority;0:,6:scheme;4:http,6:method;4:POST,4:port;5:11434#4:host;20:host.docker.internal;13:timestamp_end;18:1784456200.6829422^15:timestamp_start;18:1784456200.6817052^8:trailers;0:~7:content;2019:{"model": "qwen3:4b-instruct", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "### Task:\nSuggest 3-5 relevant follow-up questions or prompts that the user might naturally ask next in this conversation as a **user**, based on the chat history, to help continue or deepen the discussion.\n### Guidelines:\n- Write all follow-up questions from the user\u2019s point of view, directed to the assistant.\n- Make questions concise, clear, and directly related to the discussed topic(s).\n- Only suggest follow-ups that make sense given the chat content and do not repeat what was already covered.\n- If the conversation is very short or not specific, suggest more general (but relevant) follow-ups the user might ask.\n- Use the conversation's primary language; default to English if multilingual.\n- Response must be a JSON object with a \"follow_ups\" key containing an array of strings, no extra text or formatting.\n### Output:\nJSON format: { \"follow_ups\": [\"Question 1?\", \"Question 2?\", \"Question 3?\"] }\n### Chat History:\n<chat_history>\nUSER: \u0418\u0437\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043a\u0438 \u0438\u0437 \u044d\u0442\u0438\u0445 \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043b\u043e\u0432 \u043c\u0435\u0442\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 (\u0440\u0443\u043a\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c, \u0434\u0430\u0442\u0430 \u0432\u044b\u0433\u0440\u0443\u0437\u043a\u0438) \u0438 \u0441\u0430\u043c\u0443 \u0442\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0443 \u0441 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0437\u0430\u043a\u0446\u0438\u044f\u043c\u0438 (\u0434\u0430\u0442\u0430, \u0430\u0440\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0443\u043b, \u0441\u0442\u043e\u0438\u043c\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c). \u0418\u0433\u043d\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043a\u0438 \u0438\u0442\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0432. \u0420\u0435\u0437\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0442 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u044c \u0432 \u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435 JSON\nASSISTANT: \n</chat_history>"}], "stream": false, "options": {"num_ctx": 20000}},7:headers;221:37:4:Host,26:host.docker.internal:11434,]36:12:Content-Type,16:application/json,]15:6:Accept,3:*/*,]40:15:Accept-Encoding,17:gzip, deflate, br,]44:10:User-Agent,26:Python/3.11 aiohttp/3.13.5,]25:14:Content-Length,4:2019,]]12:http_version;8:HTTP/1.1,}6:backup;0:~17:timestamp_created;18:1784456200.6819184^7:comment;0:;8:metadata;0:}6:marked;0:;9:is_replay;0:~11:intercepted;5:false!11:server_conn;489:3:via;0:~19:timestamp_tcp_setup;17:1784455952.044457^7:address;32:20:host.docker.internal;5:11434#]19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;18:1784456231.3314502^15:timestamp_start;18:1784455952.0372493^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:cipher;0:~11:alpn_offers;0:]4:alpn;0:~16:certificate_list;0:]3:tls;5:false!5:error;0:~18:transport_protocol;3:tcp;2:id;36:1c90719d-9199-4782-a6e9-66b76d537501;8:sockname;22:10:172.17.0.3;5:42704#]8:peername;26:14:192.168.65.254;5:11434#]}11:client_conn;457:10:proxy_mode;41:reverse:http://host.docker.internal:11434;8:mitmcert;0:~19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;17:1784456231.330015^15:timestamp_start;18:1784455952.0346532^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:cipher;0:~11:alpn_offers;0:]4:alpn;0:~16:certificate_list;0:]3:tls;5:false!5:error;0:~18:transport_protocol;3:tcp;2:id;36:ab589998-395c-4ed0-bfe0-48e92419fa39;8:sockname;21:10:172.17.0.3;4:8080#]8:peername;22:10:172.17.0.1;5:43356#]}5:error;0:~2:id;36:175f13e2-fd92-42c4-9535-2f5223757039;4:type;4:http;7:version;2:21#}4204:9:websocket;0:~8:response;708:6:reason;2:OK,11:status_code;3:200#13:timestamp_end;18:1784456213.3939989^15:timestamp_start;18:1784456213.3930984^8:trailers;0:~7:content;395:{"model":"qwen3:4b-instruct","created_at":"2026-07-19T10:16:53.3981015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":"{\n  \"tags\": [\n    \"Business\",\n    \"Data\",\n    \"Information Extraction\"\n  ]\n}"},"done":true,"done_reason":"stop","total_duration":3408486800,"load_duration":118737900,"prompt_eval_count":245,"prompt_eval_duration":1854561000,"eval_count":23,"eval_duration":1415042000},7:headers;127:51:12:Content-Type,31:application/json; charset=utf-8,]40:4:Date,29:Sun, 19 Jul 2026 10:16:53 GMT,]24:14:Content-Length,3:395,]]12:http_version;8:HTTP/1.1,}7:request;2246:4:path;9:/api/chat,9:authority;0:,6:scheme;4:http,6:method;4:POST,4:port;5:11434#4:host;20:host.docker.internal;13:timestamp_end;18:1784456209.9811654^15:timestamp_start;17:1784456209.980136^8:trailers;0:~7:content;1762:{"model": "qwen3:4b-instruct", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "### Task:\nGenerate 1-3 broad tags categorizing the main themes of the chat history, along with 1-3 more specific subtopic tags.\n\n### Guidelines:\n- Start with high-level domains (e.g. Science, Technology, Philosophy, Arts, Politics, Business, Health, Sports, Entertainment, Education)\n- Consider including relevant subfields/subdomains if they are strongly represented throughout the conversation\n- If content is too short (less than 3 messages) or too diverse, use only [\"General\"]\n- Use the chat's primary language; default to English if multilingual\n- Prioritize accuracy over specificity\n\n### Output:\nJSON format: { \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\", \"tag3\"] }\n\n### Chat History:\n<chat_history>\nUSER: \u0418\u0437\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043a\u0438 \u0438\u0437 \u044d\u0442\u0438\u0445 \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043b\u043e\u0432 \u043c\u0435\u0442\u0430\u0434\u0430\u043d\u043d\u044b\u0435 (\u0440\u0443\u043a\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0434\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c, \u0434\u0430\u0442\u0430 \u0432\u044b\u0433\u0440\u0443\u0437\u043a\u0438) \u0438 \u0441\u0430\u043c\u0443 \u0442\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u0443 \u0441 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0437\u0430\u043a\u0446\u0438\u044f\u043c\u0438 (\u0434\u0430\u0442\u0430, \u0430\u0440\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0443\u043b, \u0441\u0442\u043e\u0438\u043c\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c). \u0418\u0433\u043d\u043e\u0440\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0439 \u0441\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043a\u0438 \u0438\u0442\u043e\u0433\u043e\u0432. \u0420\u0435\u0437\u0443\u043b\u044c\u0442\u0430\u0442 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0441\u0442\u0430\u0432\u044c \u0432 \u0432\u0438\u0434\u0435 JSON\nASSISTANT: \n</chat_history>"}], "stream": false, "options": {"num_ctx": 20000}},7:headers;221:37:4:Host,26:host.docker.internal:11434,]36:12:Content-Type,16:application/json,]15:6:Accept,3:*/*,]40:15:Accept-Encoding,17:gzip, deflate, br,]44:10:User-Agent,26:Python/3.11 aiohttp/3.13.5,]25:14:Content-Length,4:1762,]]12:http_version;8:HTTP/1.1,}6:backup;0:~17:timestamp_created;18:1784456209.9803317^7:comment;0:;8:metadata;0:}6:marked;0:;9:is_replay;0:~11:intercepted;5:false!11:server_conn;489:3:via;0:~19:timestamp_tcp_setup;17:1784455952.044457^7:address;32:20:host.docker.internal;5:11434#]19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;18:1784456231.3314502^15:timestamp_start;18:1784455952.0372493^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:cipher;0:~11:alpn_offers;0:]4:alpn;0:~16:certificate_list;0:]3:tls;5:false!5:error;0:~18:transport_protocol;3:tcp;2:id;36:1c90719d-9199-4782-a6e9-66b76d537501;8:sockname;22:10:172.17.0.3;5:42704#]8:peername;26:14:192.168.65.254;5:11434#]}11:client_conn;457:10:proxy_mode;41:reverse:http://host.docker.internal:11434;8:mitmcert;0:~19:timestamp_tls_setup;0:~13:timestamp_end;17:1784456231.330015^15:timestamp_start;18:1784455952.0346532^3:sni;0:~11:tls_version;0:~11:cipher_list;0:]6:ci